note right of Calculator
  divide raises ValueError on b == 0
  factorial raises TypeError for non-int,
    ValueError for negative n
  square_root raises ValueError for x < 0
  log / ln raise ValueError for x <= 0
  Failed operations are not recorded
    in history; only successful ones are.
  All error conditions are logged at ERROR
    level via module-level logger.
end note

